{"tid":1632162,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"急！！英文文宣","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:44:21.000Z","uid":71831,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"92392738098350cc1c3c2a9f0a1db4a6444ba2b1","tid":1632162,"uid":71831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:07:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KRgoPKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKRgoPKE.jpg&h=29a1ca9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好明顯而家政府玩抹黑 煽風點火<br />\n唔該文宣 twitter做野<br />\n大家加油"},{"pid":"8717d8a04418d01fa15a6959f05a19c143447f15","tid":1632162,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:10:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係外國既香港人都可以一齊係連登出力！ 而家只係要你入黎推post</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n4.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">外國巴打可以幫手文宣，尤其exchange學生，仲可以介紹俾其他國家既人</span></strong></span><br />\n5.擴大和理非平台，快速文宣，一個巴絲可翻譯，另一巴絲亦可做搬運工，快速輸出文宣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"3d3b650ad1d092d580169c51836ea8353cd915c2","tid":1632162,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:10:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[18區開花] 一句講晒，聽日一點定八點？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631933</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"},{"pid":"7d2a3d4bd42702445515b11a4154f6b71eb11587","tid":1632162,"uid":331388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:10:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb6f52a4a77ef5834c347db57098b0d1cdbc6517","tid":1632162,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:13:40.000Z","msg":"推俾外國旅客 咪俾黨鐵賺錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632118\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632118</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"965a6d3a951bda817746cda709aae294807cd6b6","tid":1632162,"uid":264956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:17:09.000Z","msg":"比cctvb拍劇用架，到時又有剪輯版本架喇！"},{"pid":"9ec2aa3b7b76d7405696b4d30b3216b2c6d6dea9","tid":1632162,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:19:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15900f08927e43dec0a03dffdaab340d929c5a6a","tid":1632162,"uid":71831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a3db067078726fbe59dc4a2352c117a4a6a97eb","tid":1632162,"uid":331388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:44:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}